                                    img(src=`/assets/img/portfolio/thumb/petfinder-5.webp` alt='petfinder' title='petfinder' loading='lazy' class="img-fluid rounded")

            // Role & Impact
            .project-section.role-section
                h5.section-title
                    i.fas.fa-user-tie.me-2
                    | Role & Impact
                
                .row
                    .col-md-6
                        .responsibility-card
                            h6
                                i.fas.fa-code.me-2
                                | Full-Stack Development
                            ul.responsibility-list
                                li Built the entire platform from scratch using Laravel and MySQL
                                li Developed custom logic for PDF poster generation and image processing
                                li Implemented interactive maps for pet sighting locations
                                li Managed end-to-end development cycle from concept to deployment
                    
                    .col-md-6
                        .responsibility-card
                            h6
                                i.fas.fa-search.me-2
                                | SEO & Performance
                            ul.responsibility-list
                                li Implemented advanced SEO strategies for higher search visibility
                                li Optimized page load speeds for better mobile user experience
                                li Integrated social media sharing hooks for viral reach
                                li Established automated backup and maintenance routines

